data.description: Welcome to your dream home in Brenham, Texas—a 3 bed, 2 bath sanctuary on 6+ acres, designed for modern living and outdoor bliss. Recently refreshed with new paint, lighting, and updated kitchen and baths, this home captures comfort and style. Benefit from additional spaces like a dedicated office/4th bedroom and formal dining room, designed to accommodate many different circumstances.    Tucked in the very back of Bluebonnet Hills, the 6.3 acres of land features over 30 feet of elevation change from front to back and boasts miles long views right as you drive in.  The private pond could be cultivated into a fisherman’s dream and there’s even access to a large community pond as well.  There’s ample space for pastures; great for 4h projects or even just pasture pets!    Strategically located minutes from Hwy 290 and just over 30 mins from the Grand Pkwy, this property truly has it all.    Don't miss this unparalleled opportunity to live your Texas dream. Come see it today!
